{"tid":1821321,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"搵車先? 搵車位先?","createTime":"2020-01-12T07:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T01:43:32.000Z","uid":79410,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"cf7b786fc6a90d61d888d4aaf17a845d226b201e","tid":1821321,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T07:37:14.000Z","msg":"想買假日車(唔介意泊遠D), 但係買咗又唔知放邊. 係咪求其租住D 貴價車場先? 之後再搵?<br />\n如果租咗車場先.(其實有冇得未買車就租定先?), 又唔知幾耐先睇啱心水買車<br />\n其實有冇D 車位出租網? 搵嚟搵去都係好鬼分散. 唔知點搵車位. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22b247d89cfd24dd4f35a2e1b9e78b352c74db7","tid":1821321,"uid":48611,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T07:46:12.000Z","msg":"拍街"},{"pid":"1d3e11462fb0436c6da6571cdad4cee4a7f09cb4","tid":1821321,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T07:52:20.000Z","msg":"假日車就唔好泊街 <br />\n你一個星期有5日係24小時等抄喎, 好易中<br />\n月租場咪行入去個場問囉<br />\n私人租位咪上網囉 搵位易都有唔少盤<br />\n錢多咪搵地產佬 一般收你半個月租金做佣"},{"pid":"f8dc7c77a265f5a457f643a9dc37ba225ba62a07","tid":1821321,"uid":102187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T07:52:41.000Z","msg":"邊區？<br />\n有錢就解決到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa4c6b4e090668bb579f5bb93548de64c26a07a","tid":1821321,"uid":266100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:24:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47084268fa3f6cf6d77751cba76d52da7902f06d","tid":1821321,"uid":79013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:39:51.000Z","msg":"房署場要有牌簿、行車証副本先可以申請。其他私人場可以淨係報車牌就申請得，建議直接去停車場問，始終每個場都唔同規則"},{"pid":"837afb094a40c329a10784ec537fa186cdfd6e8c","tid":1821321,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8dc7c77a265f5a457f643a9dc37ba225ba62a07","tid":1821321,"uid":102187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T07:52:41.000Z","msg":"邊區？<br />\n有錢就解決到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif